{"pageProps":{"metadata":{"title":"Python基礎文法 - 後期","curriculumId":"16c2297f-7a72-803f-872e-ef1fab8e273e","category":"後期","visibility":["基礎班","発展班"],"tags":["基礎班","Python"],"is_basic_curriculum":true,"id":"11"},"mdBlocks":[{"type":"paragraph","blockId":"16c2297f-7a72-81dd-92ca-c37bb79a1cd5","parent":"今回はpythonの`lambda`式について説明します。","children":[]},{"blockId":"16c2297f-7a72-8170-bdd1-c278dedf2ecc","type":"heading_2","parent":"## lambda式の基本","children":[]},{"blockId":"16c2297f-7a72-8106-96ee-fb1308c998ea","type":"divider","parent":"---","children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","blockId":"16c2297f-7a72-816b-b9a8-f17e62284c06","parent":"`lambda`式は、関数を作るための短縮記法です。通常の関数定義と異なり、`lambda`式は一行で書け、関数名を省略することができます。","children":[]},{"blockId":"16c2297f-7a72-81f5-a40b-ced203f85dc3","type":"callout","parent":"> 基本構文  \n> ```python  \n> lambda 引数:処理内容  \n> ```","children":[{"blockId":"16c2297f-7a72-81fe-b293-cf6bc434a48f","type":"code","parent":"```python\nlambda 引数:処理内容\n```","children":[]}]},{"blockId":"16c2297f-7a72-8129-93eb-e6e275884e51","type":"bulleted_list_item","parent":"- **引数**: 関数に渡す引数。","children":[]},{"blockId":"16c2297f-7a72-81bb-9f50-cf59aad56e4e","type":"bulleted_list_item","parent":"- **式**: 関数が返す結果（通常、1つの式のみ）。","children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","blockId":"16c2297f-7a72-8167-b7bb-f7576a7a4543","parent":"引数がない場合は引数の部分に`_`（アンダーバー）を使います","children":[]},{"blockId":"16c2297f-7a72-81f2-81b4-e9ae1be8b92b","type":"callout","parent":"> 引数がない場合  \n> ```python  \n> lambda _:処理内容  \n> ```","children":[{"blockId":"16c2297f-7a72-810a-924f-e27d5ba51bb0","type":"code","parent":"```python\nlambda _:処理内容\n```","children":[]}]},{"blockId":"16c2297f-7a72-81c2-8779-c0e0a81da4a6","type":"heading_2","parent":"## 使用例","children":[]},{"blockId":"16c2297f-7a72-81fa-a050-cf77fcbc8ece","type":"divider","parent":"---","children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","blockId":"16c2297f-7a72-8124-8e5f-ca35e4a74a18","parent":"lambda式の具体的な使用例を示します。","children":[]},{"blockId":"16c2297f-7a72-810e-843b-d86afac2bbc0","type":"callout","parent":"> 2つの引数を受け取って、その和を返す関数  \n> ```python  \n> add = lambda x, y: x + y  \n> print(add(3, 5))  # 8  \n> ```","children":[{"blockId":"16c2297f-7a72-810a-9d7f-c8b659b551e8","type":"code","parent":"```python\nadd = lambda x, y: x + y\nprint(add(3, 5))  # 8\n```","children":[]}]},{"blockId":"16c2297f-7a72-8183-bc27-ec1f4d862208","type":"callout","parent":"> リスト内の各要素を2倍にする関数  \n> ```python  \n> nums = [1, 2, 3, 4]  \n> doubled = list(map(lambda x: x * 2, nums))  \n> print(doubled)  # [2, 4, 6, 8]  \n> ```","children":[{"blockId":"16c2297f-7a72-8191-9aad-d862fa7b436d","type":"code","parent":"```python\nnums = [1, 2, 3, 4]\ndoubled = list(map(lambda x: x * 2, nums))\nprint(doubled)  # [2, 4, 6, 8]\n```","children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","blockId":"16c2297f-7a72-81ab-b233-ca2750a6a650","parent":"","children":[]}],"pageNavs":[{"title":"Home","id":"/posts"},{"title":"基礎班カリキュラム","id":"/posts/course/basic"},{"title":"後期","id":"/posts/course/後期"},{"title":"Python基礎文法 - 後期","id":"/posts/curriculums/16c2297f-7a72-803f-872e-ef1fab8e273e/16c2297f-7a72-803f-872e-ef1fab8e273e"},{"id":"/posts/curriculums/16c2297f-7a72-803f-872e-ef1fab8e273e/16c2297f-7a72-8078-a47f-ea63c981db9b","title":"lambda式"}],"childrenData":{"title":"Python基礎文法 - 後期","childPages":[{"title":"import文","id":"16c2297f-7a72-80e6-9c8c-cfea39a9aee2"},{"title":"クラスの継承","id":"16c2297f-7a72-80aa-8f18-cca16f8b3361"},{"title":"文字列の中に変数を埋め込む","id":"16c2297f-7a72-80b7-b6f8-f38868675030"},{"title":"lambda式","id":"16c2297f-7a72-8078-a47f-ea63c981db9b"},{"title":"例外処理","id":"16c2297f-7a72-80b3-a867-f9e842f141de"}]},"pageId":"16c2297f-7a72-8078-a47f-ea63c981db9b"},"__N_SSG":true}